        "timestamp": "2018-09-06 05:44:42.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIn dataRestoreSnapshot.sh, line 47, I removed \"$2\", in order for the java function to clear out the AAI DB.\nexecute_spring_jar org.onap.aai.dbgen.DataSnapshot ${PROJECT_HOME}/resources/etc/appprops/dataSnapshot-logback.xml \"CLEAR_ENTIRE_DATABASE\" \"$1\" \"$2\"\nto be\nexecute_spring_jar org.onap.aai.dbgen.DataSnapshot ${PROJECT_HOME}/resources/etc/appprops/dataSnapshot-logback.xml \"CLEAR_ENTIRE_DATABASE\" \"$1\"\nIf we call the function org.onap.aai.dbgen.DataSnapshot with \"command + $1 + $2\", the function will use the default action \"JUST_TAKE_SNAPSHOT\" only, instead of the correct action \"CLEAR_ENTIRE_DATABASE\"",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
